tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review:
Thank you Dr. Sanjay Mohanchandra for the great experience, and quality work you have done on my teeth. I wanted to take a moment to share my feedback regarding the recent dental surgery experience I had under your care. Overall, I appreciate the level of professionalism and expertise demonstrated by you and your team.

I am usually apprehensive about needles, and it was no sweat at all. Your calming and reassuring demeanor before the surgery greatly eased my anxiety. Throughout the process, I felt confident in your abilities in dental implants and surgery.

I also appreciate the cleanliness of your practice was noteworthy. It created a comfortable and hygienic environment, contributing to a positive overall experience. Your staff members were courteous and professional, creating a welcoming atmosphere. This positive interaction with your team enhanced the overall experience.

Thanks again! My family and I have been pleased with your professional, yet personable, service. See you soon.
